snippet.title: Stormterror Dvalin 「Caelestinum Finale Termini」 Piano Performance / Mondstadt Weekly Boss OST
snippet.description:
Genshin Impact - Stormterror Dvalin Boss Fight OST 「Caelestinum Finale Termini」 Piano Performance


Today's performance is 'Caelestinum Finale Termini', the boss battle theme of Dvalin the Stormterror, the first weekly boss in Genshin Impact.

It boasted a level of difficulty that was not easy at the time and a unique gimmick.
It was also a boss that was loved by many users due to its magnificent and beautiful OST.

It may be a little late, but the composer of this song, Chief Sound Director Genshin Impact, ‘Yu-peng-Chen’ has left HoYo-Mix.
So at least within the Hoyoverse, We will no longer be able to listen to this person's music.

I thought that one day I would like to put a lot of effort into making this beautiful song into my own performance piece.
With a sense of respect and wishing the composer good luck in the future,
I got to play a song I had cherished for a long time.
I plan to create several more performance pieces with this intention in the future.

In addition, in this performance, as it was a song that I especially cherished, I not only played the piano, but also created a string session for some sections and played it together.
I put a lot of effort into it, but I don't know if you'll enjoy it.

Thank you for listening.

Twitch Streaming : https://www.twitch.tv/frost_piano
